INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2015-11-10 16:37:04','2015-11-10 16:37:04','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','closed','open','','sample-page','','','2015-11-10 16:37:04','2015-11-10 16:37:04','',0,'http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(8,2,'2015-11-04 22:40:00','2015-11-04 22:40:00','<img style=\"float: left; height: 320px; width: 256px;\" src=\"http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/received_102038167503785161-240x300.jpeg\" alt=\"\" hspace=\"10\" />      The learning is coming along and I am starting to understand more and more.  It was so great to get so many emails and letters this week.  I still have to work hard but talking with the native missionaries is helping a lot, they are very patient and helpful.\r\n\r\nFor recreation we play lots of ping pong and volleyball.  I have been loosing some weight so I need to go and see the CCM doctor this week, but not to worry, I had some to spare. The food is getting better as my standards are getting lower!\r\n\r\nI have been singing in the choir, it is all in Spanish so that is helping also with learning more and more.  I spoke in our branch this week as well, it was kinda hard, but you know I killed it!\r\n\r\nThis week we got to leave the CCM compound and go to the Mexico City Temple it was so nice to be out and seeing the city.  I loved the temple and being able to go.  Part of the session was in English and part in Spanish so that was awesome.\r\n\r\nWell I have a hard time understanding what people are saying and with reading right now and as we went in to meet with our first investigator I said a prayer a really hard prayer and I went into the room and as she began to speak to us, really fast by the way. I understood, not translated to English understood, I just knew what she was saying and started to talk back with her in Spanish.  I don\'t remember what I said but I could feel the spirit so strong and then I read her Helaman 10:5 which is so long in Spanish and i didn\'t have any problems it was a true miracle.\r\nI love getting letters so keep them coming, it helps keep my spirits up.  I have sent some pictures.  Love you all very much.\r\nyo se la expacion es por todal personas y la amor de Dios en infenyado. yo amor mí family mucho mas\r\n<div><img class=\"\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/AQlDQzIrogdflB0juMhcCaHIQ2cUsuP43C32OGuNQ5cLyAaeq3nORXET3StYk9OErsrN2bYoA0e7R1zQ_O_WHTaNc08zvkMGE_NKxYHL1g4JcVNu-ArdRmBXSe9SxdKGt0KZPMC2BlC-wG3IGdiUIHwsAk5sqVJSEkDxNmI4h8q2wa-e8XfLWWoG1qBWGmFhetDWl425xSmqcITeD_Pgx9GsOufIW-DBjvFtkIpgHIVuyO08piOWPoRTwOlP3Oay0_CFfAD1UaJT5gDuZ1F3OCF1-WBNdC6V_mCfk7j4-FXdyWGrqm5GKG3D7_erSAx3iWIdGnXaf2f6sI4d4GZlrbeYPrSNBHP14ZCYajcgmN060GIC4V8Bku3zSTJbZk6oEha2P_qizmOVJ584XdJe61ROQpsgpmoqs7jqubmoOVS5utKz-mA8RcmtCXat-8KZnThGaitWX1rZKkxYo2DgbXzA4OkY470B1Zu3z1OAf8fF-szXO8p8tgD_LA3T7iVaTspv_nroxj58-wUOuhyDAXPNdNxkcxe2E_BVwHs8lcI=w1696-h955-no\" alt=\"\" width=\"1347\" height=\"757\" /></div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>\r\n<table style=\"float: left; margin-right: 1em; text-align