ther missionaries. &nbsp;I have made wonderful friends already, and excited to be able to go into the mission field with them. &nbsp;</div><div style=\"background-color: white; color: #141823; display: inline; font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 19.32px;\"><div style=\"margin-bottom: 6px;\">Please continue to pray for me as I study Spanish, that I will be able to pick up the language quickly. Please pray that I will have patience. &nbsp;</div><div style=\"margin-bottom: 6px; margin-top: 6px;\">Love you all<br />Elder Finlayson</div></div>','\"There is lots and lots of Spanish here!\"','','inherit','closed','closed','','9-revision-v1','','','2015-10-26 14:18:00','2015-10-26 14:18:00','',9,'http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/?p=13',0,'revision','',0),(14,1,'2015-11-10 17:40:43','2015-11-10 17:40:43','','mexico-mtc-sign','','inherit','open','closed','','mexico-mtc-sign','','','2015-11-10 17:40:43','2015-11-10 17:40:43','',10,'http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/mexico-mtc-sign.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(15,1,'2015-11-10 17:40:44','2015-11-10 17:40:44','','dsc_0013','','inherit','open','closed','','dsc_0013','','','2015-11-10 17:40:44','2015-11-10 17:40:44','',10,'http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/dsc_0013.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(16,1,'2015-11-10 17:40:45','2015-11-10 17:40:45','','dsc_0018','','inherit','open','closed','','dsc_0018','','','2015-11-10 17:40:45','2015-11-10 17:40:45','',10,'http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/dsc_0018.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(17,1,'2015-11-10 17:40:45','2015-11-10 17:40:45','','dsc_0014','','inherit','open','closed','','dsc_0014','','','2015-11-10 17:40:45','2015-11-10 17:40:45','',10,'http://ke5zwg.webhop.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/dsc_0014.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(18,1,'2015-11-10 17:40:46','2015-11-10 17:40:46','','dsc_0021','','inherit','open','closed','','dsc_0021','','','2015-11-10 17:40:46','2015-11-10 17:40:4