 is here on the blog along with an email address. &nbsp;</div><div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;\">We don\'t know much but that he arrived, said that he was safe and asked for us to write letters. &nbsp;</div><div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;\">We are grateful that he is willing to serve the Lord and the people of Mexico. &nbsp;Your prayers on his behalf in learning the language would be great. &nbsp;There is great power in prayer. &nbsp;</div><div style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em; text-align: left;\">His Prep Day will be on Thursday while in the CCM so we will send updates as we get them.&nbsp;</div><div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-q7wr6DR_CBU/ViGKn_atlrI/AAAAAAAALVg/xexmslXyBRg/s1600/dsc_0013.jpg\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"263\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-q7wr6DR_CBU/ViGKn_atlrI/AAAAAAAALVg/xexmslXyBRg/s400/dsc_0013.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div><div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"></div><div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-H8ZcAVjPppM/ViGKnzPDXJI/AAAAAAAALVc/ZDzzfbfsb8k/s1600/dsc_0018.jpg\" style=\"clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"131\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-H8ZcAVjPppM/ViGKnzPDXJI/AAAAAAAALVc/ZDzzfbfsb8k/s200/dsc_0018.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></a></div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9Cob6LOB02o/ViGKn49qTOI/AAAAAAAALVY/tXUOOW9F9Uo/s1600/dsc_0014.jpg\" style=\"clear: left; float: left; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"131\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-9Cob6LOB02o/ViGKn49qTOI/AAAAAAAALVY/tXUOOW9F9Uo/s200/dsc_0014.jpg\" width=\"200\" /></a><br /><div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\">Elder Finlayson with Nana &amp; Papa</div><div style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-