 ya its been really good we all love each other and love to tell jokes, quote movies, and we all love to learn!\r\n\r\nOne of my goals is idk how to say it in English any more but le amor de jesucristo por todos personas we are asked to stop translating and just take the words in Spanish for what they are lol buy mí corezón we todos por me familia mí amor ustedes mucho.\r\n\r\nOur devos are the best, we watch church sponsored  movies on Sunday nights and devos on Tuesday nights they are so cool. We watched one devo that Elder Holland did in Provo a few years ago and we joked that he took the grill in there and flipped some burgers having a good time then just threw the grill on the missionaries and grilled them. He went so hard and really got in our faces. And for another one we had the head of the missionary department, that was really cool he talked about following the white hand book and the Lord will watch out for us.  Every time a missionary gets sent home on medical he says he gets an email and he can turn to the page in the \"white bible\" that talks about that very action. (Here is a link to the talk by Elder Holland that he liked so much.  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qRCYJF9mrD0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qRCYJF9mrD0</a> )\r\n\r\nOur new companions don\'t talk to us but we love playing soccer with the natives at gym. I am at 4 goals 7 blocks in soccer and like 12 kills and 7 block kills in vollyball I am killing it.\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_52\" align=\"aligncenter\" width=\"326\"]<a href=\"http://www.elderfinlayson.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cris-1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-52\" src=\"http://www.elderfinlayson.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/cris-1-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"cris (1)\" width=\"326\" height=\"217\" /></a> Elder Finlayson\'s District at the Mexico City Temple[/caption]\r\n\r\nI love ya\'ll so much and will talk to ya\"ll next week much love keep praying there are a lot of blessings from it!\r\n\r\n